unk_28bc3c5.value:
function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)

	if not Hydra.ActorIsValid(idPrisoner) then 
		return 
	end
	
	bPrisonerFreed = true
	Hydra.Wait(.25)
	
	if not Hydra.ActorIsValid(idPrisoner) then 
		return 
	end
	
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idPrisoner, ID_WALK_TO_POS, "NPC_Walk", false)
	Hydra.QActorFaceActor(idPrisoner, idActorPlayer)
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(idPrisoner)
	
	if SELECTION == eRunAway then
		Hydra.TreasureClassDropAtActorForPlayer(idPrisoner, S_TREASURECLASS, idActorPlayer)
		Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(CONV_RUN, idPrisoner)
		Hydra.Wait(1)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idPrisoner, ID_RUN_TO_POS, "NPC_Run", false)
		Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(idPrisoner, 1)
	elseif SELECTION == eFollower then
		Hydra.QActorPlaySimpleConversation(CONV_FOLLOWER, idPrisoner)
		Hydra.ActorSetFollowTarget(idPrisoner, idActorPlayer, Hydra.FOLLOW_TYPE_DEFAULT)
		Hydra.ActorSetLoadout(idPrisoner, S_ITEM_SWORD, S_ITEM_SHIELD)
	end
	Hydra.ActorClearAnimSetOverride(idPrisoner)
	Hydra.ActorSetInvulnerable(idPrisoner,false)
	Hydra.ActorSetTargetable(idPrisoner,true)
	Hydra.ActorSetAnimSetOverride(idPrisoner, "NPC_Combat_1HSSHD")
	Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idPrisoner,true)
	Hydra.ActorSetFollowTarget(idPrisoner, idActorPlayer, Hydra.FOLLOW_TYPE_DEFAULT)
end

	if not Hydra.ActorIsValid(idPrisoner) or bPrisonerFreed then 
		return
	end

-- Event Generic Data
ID_THIS_QUEST = Hydra.QuestGetOwner()
eFollower = "Follower"
eRunAway = "RunAway"
tEnums = {eFollower, eRunAway}
bPrisonerFreed = false
bPrisonerFreed = false
bPlayCalloutVO = false
nTimeToPlayVO = 0

--changed to only roll for followers based on feedback
SELECTION = tEnums[Hydra.GetRandomInt(1, 1)]

--S_CONV_CALLOUT = Hydra.ReferenceConversation("CAMP_Step_Cannibal_Prnr_Help")

if SELECTION == eFollower then
	if Hydra.GetRandomInt(1, 2) == 1 then
		S_ACTOR_TO_SPAWN = Hydra.ReferenceActor("CMP_Hawe_Crusader_Prisoner_Follower_M")
	else
		S_ACTOR_TO_SPAWN = Hydra.ReferenceActor("CMP_Hawe_Crusader_Prisoner_Follower_F")
	end

elseif SELECTION == eRunAway then
	if Hydra.GetRandomInt(1,2) == 1 then
		S_ACTOR_TO_SPAWN = Hydra.ReferenceActor("CMP_Hawe_Crusader_Prisoner_RunAway_M")
	else
		S_ACTOR_TO_SPAWN = Hydra.ReferenceActor("CMP_Hawe_Crusader_Prisoner_RunAway_F")
	end
	S_TREASURECLASS = Hydra.ReferenceTreasureClass("Gizmo_Reward_CorpseAdventurer")
	S_AISTATE = Hydra.ReferenceAIState("EVT_Monster_RunToRandomPosAndFade")
end
